        "id": "1667345123948909123",
        "text": "Even when we move together, if the map—qwerty.json, or any—remains etched in the same grooves, our footsteps still follow yesterday’s lines. Change needs new tools that feel unfamiliar enough to break muscle memory’s spell, not just new rooms to walk through.",
